{"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are no steps needed to migrate to 1.16 of the Composable Architecture, but there has been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a change to the underlying behavior of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".appStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" that one should be aware of. When using"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".appStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Shared"},{"type":"text","text":", if your key does not contain the characters “.” or “@”, then changes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to that key in ","type":"text"},{"code":"UserDefaults","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be observed using key-value observing (KVO).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Otherwise, ","type":"text"},{"code":"NotificationCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be used to observe changes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KVO is a far more efficient way of observing changes to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UserDefaults"},{"type":"text","text":" and it works cross-process,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as from widgets and app extensions. However, KVO does not work when the keys contain “.”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or “@”, and so in those cases we must use the cruder tool of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NotificationCenter"},{"type":"text","text":". That is not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as efficient, and it forces us to perform a thread-hop when the notification is posted before"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"we can update the ","type":"text"},{"code":"@Shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" value. For this reason it is not possible to animate changes that are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"made directly to ","type":"text"},{"code":"UserDefaults","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["withAnimation {","  \/\/ ⚠️ This will not animate any SwiftUI views using '@Shared(.appStorage(\"co.pointfree.count\"))'","  UserDefaults.standard.set(0, forKey: \"co.pointfree.count\")","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In general, we recommend using other delimeters for your keys, such as “\/”, “:”, “-”, etc.:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["@Shared(.appStorage(\"co:pointfree:count\")) var count = 0"]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}],"role":"article","title":"Migrating to 1.16"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.19","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.18","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.12","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.11","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.10","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.9","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.8","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.7","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.6","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.5","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.4"]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.16","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"code":".appStorage","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" strategy used with "},{"code":"@Shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" now uses key-value observing instead of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"NotificationCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" when possible. Learn how this may affect your code."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.16"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture/MigratingTo1.8":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.8","abstract":[{"text":"Update your code to make use of the new capabilities of the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Reducer()","type":"reference"},{"text":" macro, including automatic","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"fulfillment of requirements for destination reducers and path reducers.","type":"text"}],"kind":"article","type":"topic","title":"Migrating to 1.8","role":"article","url":"\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.8"},"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture/MigratingTo1.14":{